{"id":15343,"date":"2022-12-13T10:26:14","date_gmt":"2022-12-13T03:26:14","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/?p=15343"},"modified":"2022-12-13T10:26:14","modified_gmt":"2022-12-13T03:26:14","slug":"huong-dan-tao-quang-cao-zalo-official-account","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/huong-dan-tao-quang-cao-zalo-official-account.html\/","title":{"rendered":"H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn t\u1ea1o qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Zalo Official Account"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Zalo Official Account l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1o qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng quan t\u00e2m, t\u0103ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u trang Zalo Official Account c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p, c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng. Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1ebd hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb lu\u00e2n phi\u00ean tr\u00ean Zalo app (Zalo News Feed, Zalo Article) v\u00e0 Zalo Network (bao g\u1ed3m ZingMP3, BaoMoi, ZingNews \u2026)<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Zalo Official Account, nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o truy c\u1eadp v\u00e0o trang Zalo Ads v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n theo c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y<\/p>\n<p><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: Thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng v\u00e0o trang\u00a0<strong>T\u1ea1o Qu\u1ea3ng C\u00e1o<\/strong>\u00a0&gt;&gt; ch\u1ecdn lo\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch\u00a0<strong>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Zalo Official Account<\/strong>\u00a0&gt;&gt; Nh\u1ea5n\u00a0<strong>B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: \u0110\u1eb7t t\u00ean chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn t\u00e0i OA qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Ch\u1ecdn t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Official Account th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o trong danh s\u00e1ch ch\u1ee7 t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n l\u00e0 Admin ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e2n quy\u1ec1n qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd, \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00e0 nh\u1ea5n n\u00fat\u00a0<strong>T\u1ea1o qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: Nh\u1eafm ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>1. \u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>&gt;&gt; \u0110\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m, ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t trong hai l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>T\u1ec9nh, Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1, Qu\u1eadn, Huy\u1ec7n:<\/strong>\u00a0ch\u1ecdn t\u1ec9nh th\u00e0nh theo v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ecba l\u00fd: Mi\u1ec1n B\u1eafc, Mi\u1ec1n Trung, Mi\u1ec1n Nam<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15344\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15344\" style=\"width: 646px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15344 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Nhom-doi-tuong-1.png\" alt=\"Vi-tri-quang-cao\" width=\"646\" height=\"418\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Nhom-doi-tuong-1.png 646w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Nhom-doi-tuong-1-300x194.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 646px) 100vw, 646px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15344\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">V\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1eb7t qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/dd>\n<dd><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>V\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3:<\/strong>\u00a0\u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1, t\u1ec9nh th\u00e0nh ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&gt;&gt; \u0110\u1ec3 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n ho\u1eb7c m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng ph\u1ea1m vi:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>C\u00e1ch 1:\u00a0<\/strong>Ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0o icon h\u00ecnh m\u0169i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng gi\u1ea3m ph\u1ea1m vi.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>C\u00e1ch 2:<\/strong>\u00a0Ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0o m\u0169i t\u00ean tr\u00ean \u00f4 \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c ph\u1ea1m vi b\u00e1n k\u00ednh c\u1ea7n m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng hay thu h\u1eb9p.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>2. Gi\u1edbi t\u00ednh:<\/strong>\u00a0ch\u1ecdn theo nh\u00f3m \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15345\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15345\" style=\"width: 665px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15345 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Nhom-doi-tuong-2.png\" alt=\"Nhom-doi-tuong-khach-hang-huong-toi\" width=\"665\" height=\"256\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Nhom-doi-tuong-2.png 665w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Nhom-doi-tuong-2-300x115.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 665px) 100vw, 665px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15345\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nh\u00f3m kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi<\/dd>\n<dd><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>3. N\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng:<\/strong>\u00a0ch\u1ecdn h\u1ec7 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh theo m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau.<\/p>\n<p><strong>4. \u0110\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i:\u00a0<\/strong>di chuy\u1ec3n tr\u00ean thanh \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau.<\/p>\n<p><strong>5. Ti\u00eau ch\u00ed kh\u00e1c\u00a0(Nh\u00e2n kh\u1ea9u h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 S\u1edf th\u00edch)<\/strong>: nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ch\u1ecdn th\u00f4ng tin nh\u00e2n kh\u1ea9u h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 s\u1edf th\u00edch d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng. H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng Zalo Ads s\u1ebd \u01b0u ti\u00ean ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u00f3m ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 tr\u00f9ng nh\u00f3m ti\u00eau ch\u00ed n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15346\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15346\" style=\"width: 700px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15346 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Nhom-doi-tuong-3-700x450-1.png\" alt=\"Nhan-khau-hoc-so-thich\" width=\"700\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Nhom-doi-tuong-3-700x450-1.png 700w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Nhom-doi-tuong-3-700x450-1-300x193.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15346\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nh\u00e2n kh\u1ea9u h\u1ecdc, s\u1edf th\u00edch<\/dd>\n<dd><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: Thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch v\u00e0 chi ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch\u00a0<strong>ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5p chu\u1ed9t<\/strong>\u00a0&gt;&gt;\u00a0<strong>\u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1\u00a0<\/strong>cho m\u1ed9t nh\u1ea5p chu\u1ed9t<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15348\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15348\" style=\"width: 700px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15348 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/screenshot_1600230918-1-700x222-1.png\" alt=\"Thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch v\u00e0 chi ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o\" width=\"700\" height=\"222\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/screenshot_1600230918-1-700x222-1.png 700w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/screenshot_1600230918-1-700x222-1-300x95.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15348\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch v\u00e0 chi ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><em>L\u01b0u \u00fd:\u00a0<\/em><\/strong><em>Gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5p chu\u1ed9t t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u (chi ph\u00ed click) t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c vi\u1ec7c nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ch\u1ecdn nh\u00f3m \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o m\u00e0 gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5p chu\u1ed9t s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u1ea7n linh \u0111\u1ed9ng khi \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/em><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 5: Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb n\u1ed9i dung qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb n\u1ed9i dung qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u:<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15347\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15347\" style=\"width: 700px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15347 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/QC-ZOA-700x314-1.png\" alt=\"Chuan-bi-noi-dung-quang-cao\" width=\"700\" height=\"314\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/QC-ZOA-700x314-1.png 700w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/QC-ZOA-700x314-1-300x135.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15347\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb n\u1ed9i dung qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>1. T\u00ean chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>2. H\u00ecnh m\u00f4 t\u1ea3<\/strong>: th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o. Nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i \u1ea3nh c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc\u00a0<strong>1024\u00d7533(px<\/strong>) v\u00e0 dung l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qu\u00e1 2MB.<\/p>\n<p><strong>3. Ch\u00fa th\u00edch<\/strong>\u00a0th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n n\u1ed9i dung; c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qu\u00e1 90 k\u00fd t\u1ef1<\/p>\n<p><strong>4. M\u00f4 t\u1ea3<\/strong>: th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng tin ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m. N\u1ed9i dung kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qu\u00e1 60 k\u00fd t\u1ef1<\/p>\n<p><strong>5. Th\u00f4ng tin th\u00eam<\/strong>: th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng tin gi\u00e1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ho\u1eb7c khuy\u1ebfn m\u00e3i cho s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m. N\u1ed9i dung kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qu\u00e1 60 k\u00fd t\u1ef1<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><em><strong>L\u01b0u \u00fd:\u00a0<\/strong>Nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n t\u1eeb\u00a0<\/em><strong><em>Th\u01b0 Vi\u1ec7n \u1ea2nh<\/em><\/strong><em>. Ch\u1ecdn c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f3ng to, thu nh\u1ecf ho\u1eb7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng tr\u00ean qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o.<\/em><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 6: Ch\u1ecdn Th\u00f4ng tin th\u00eam<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Cung c\u1ea5p gi\u1ea5y x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn n\u1ed9i dung qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o n\u1ebfu s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0 thu\u1ed1c, th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng, ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m\/d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 BQT Zalo Ads quy \u0111\u1ecbnh y\u00eau c\u1ea7u gi\u1ea5y ph\u00e9p t\u1ea1i\u00a0<strong>Ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/strong><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15350\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15350\" style=\"width: 700px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15350 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/TT-Them-1-700x225-1.png\" alt=\"Chon-thong-tin-them\" width=\"700\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/TT-Them-1-700x225-1.png 700w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/TT-Them-1-700x225-1-300x96.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15350\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ch\u1ecdn th\u00f4ng tin th\u00eam<\/dd>\n<dd><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 7: G\u1eedi duy\u1ec7t<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Sau khi t\u1ea1o n\u1ed9i dung qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3\u00a0nh\u1ea5n\u00a0<strong>L\u01b0u<\/strong>\u00a0n\u1ed9i dung \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda sau ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh nh\u1ea5n\u00a0<strong>G\u1eedi duy\u1ec7t<\/strong>\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb Zalo Ads ph\u00ea duy\u1ec7t qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o:<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15350\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15350\" style=\"width: 700px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15350 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/TT-Them-1-700x225-1.png\" alt=\"G\u1eedi duy\u1ec7t \" width=\"700\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/TT-Them-1-700x225-1.png 700w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/TT-Them-1-700x225-1-300x96.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15350\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">G\u1eedi duy\u1ec7t<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>1.Nh\u1ea5n\u00a0<strong>L\u01b0u\u00a0<\/strong>\u0111\u1ec3 l\u01b0u l\u1ea1i n\u1ed9i dung v\u00e0 quay l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda sau. Khi qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi duy\u1ec7t s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i\u00a0<strong>T\u1ea1o m\u1edbi<\/strong>\u00a0v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi duy\u1ec7t.<\/p>\n<p>2.Nh\u1ea5n\u00a0<strong>G\u1eedi duy\u1ec7t<\/strong>\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh Zalo Ads ki\u1ec3m tra v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh x\u00e9t duy\u1ec7t. Th\u1eddi gian duy\u1ec7t qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o trong th\u1eddi gian 30p \u2013 60p.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15351\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15351\" style=\"width: 378px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15351 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Demo-QCOA.jpg\" alt=\"Hinh-anh-quang-cao-zalo-official-Account\" width=\"378\" height=\"772\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Demo-QCOA.jpg 378w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/Demo-QCOA-147x300.jpg 147w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 378px) 100vw, 378px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15351\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Zalo Official Account<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u1edbi OA nh\u01b0 nh\u1ea5n Quan t\u00e2m, xem chi ti\u1ebft trong Official Account nh\u01b0 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, Video\u2026 gia t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3t Quan t\u00e2m, t\u1ea1o c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ecdc th\u00eam:<\/p>\n<p class=\"entry-title\"><a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/quang-cao-zalo-tep-khach-sdt.html\/\">T\u1ea1o qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Zalo v\u1edbi t\u1ec7p kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng theo S\u0110T<\/a><\/p>\n<p class=\"entry-title\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikimarketing.vn\/cach-su-dung-tu-dong-hoa-de-nang-cao.html\/\">C\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u00f3a \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao (kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m h\u1ecfng) chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Zalo Official Account l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1o qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng quan t\u00e2